description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Blind Pilot performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded August 30, 2024.

Songs:
Just a Bird 00:48
Brave 04:59
Believe Me 08:37
Jacaranda 14:37

Israel Nebeker - Lead Vox, Guitar
Ryan Dobrowski - Drums
Luke Ydstie - Vox, Bass, Mandolin
Kati Claborn - Vox, Banjo, Clarinet, Mountain Dulcimers

Host: Troy Nelson

Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Scott Holpainen, Jonathan Jacobson, Luke Knecht & Ettie Wahl
